Class Item

java.lang.Object
CsvToJsonConverter.BaseEntity
CsvToJsonConverter.Artifact
CsvToJsonConverter.Item
class Item extends Artifact
Represents a specific type of Artifact, typically a physical object with a part number. Inherits properties from Artifact and adds Item-specific fields like PartNum and ConditionNts. The entityType is set to "Item".

  • Field Details

    • partNum

      public String partNum
      The part number associated with the item. Populated from the "PartNum" CSV field. Its presence (and format) helps distinguish Items from other Artifacts.

    • conditionNts

      public String conditionNts
      Notes regarding the condition of the item. Populated from the "ConditionNts" CSV field.
